title: Fulham v Aston Villa : Rogers and Watkins on target in economic win
body_text:
PREMIER LEAGUE
Fulham v Aston Villa: Rogers and Watkins on target in economic win
Fulham 1 Aston Villa 3: Morgan Rogers, Ollie Watkins and Issa Diop’s own goal help Unai Emery’s side come from behind to claim win which lifts them up to fourth in table
